&nbsp;A man was brutally gunned down, this evening, 9 October 2016, along Ben Schoeman Street. It is believed that the man was killed in an ambush.KZNEMS and ER24 Ladymith were called to scene of the shooting, and found that the unknown man had died of his injuries. The vehicle that the man had been travelling in was riddled with bullets.Police and K9 unit have closed down the streets to conduct investigations. Motorists have been advise to seek alternative routes.More updates to following